msgctxt "chunk_D65A22CE"
msgid "Using proxy software in global mode may prevent Gradio from starting properly. For example, in [issue #77](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/77).\n"
msgstr "Die Verwendung von Proxy-Software im globalen Modus kann verhindern, dass Gradio ordnungsgemäß startet. Beispielsweise in [Issue #77](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/77).\n"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 55
msgctxt "chunk_587F7FBA"
msgid "- **Solution**:  "
msgstr "- **Lösung**:"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 56
msgctxt "chunk_E7C819A4"
msgid "Use rule mode\n"
msgstr "Verwenden Sie den Regelmodus\n"

# This content is from "Documentation-of-Translation-Services.md", line 1
msgctxt "chunk_9221A870"
msgid "[**Advanced**](./introduction.md) > **Documentation of Translation Services** _(current)_\n"
